Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;10 Methanol^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;

So you now have an ^orange;extraction lab^reset;, but aren't sure what to do with it? It's simple, really. Go place it somewhere, and toss a bunch of ^orange;logs^reset; in there. 10 should do. ^green;Bring me back 2 Methanol^reset;.
That, my friend, is how you make methanol. Now let's move on to cobblestone!
